name: Chase
body:
### You found my game

It is currently in pre-alpha and is not signed yet. if you would like to run the game just download the Chase.apk in the Case/bin folder. Please play test it and try to break it! When you do tell me so I can improve the game!


### Authors and Contributors
This project is made by @bentekkie

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with this app or found a bug? Email me at bentekkie@gmail.com
